You can use System exclusive messages to record, save and recall settings from external [[MIDI]] gear. This tutorial requires that you know how to send this information from your external device. So you will need to see it's manual.

In [[Pro Tools]]:

Go to '''Setup / MIDI / Input filter'''. Then check the boxes next to '''Only''' and '''System Exclusive'''.

Create a new MIDI track. '''Track / New / MIDI track'''.

Set the MIDI input of the MIDI track to '''All'''.

Record enable the track

In the transport right click the record button and choose '''Normal'''.

Begin recording and initiate the System Exclusive transmission on your device. 


